---
import LayoutFr from '../../layouts/LayoutFr.astro';
---

<LayoutFr title="Tarifs" description="Tarification simple et transparente pour les bases de donnees Barrel. Auto-hebergez gratuitement, payez pour le support et l'hebergement gere.">
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Tarification Simple et Transparente</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-barrel-gray/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Les deux bases de donnees sont 100% open source. Auto-hebergez gratuitement, ou obtenez du support et de l'hebergement gere.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Support Tiers Section -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-coral/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Plans de Support</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-center mb-8">Tarification par instance. Combinez selon vos besoins.</p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
          <!-- Community -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Communaute</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">Gratuit</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Pour toujours</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                100% open source
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Issues Codeberg
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Support communautaire
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://codeberg.org/barrel-platform" class="block w-full text-center bg-teal-dark/20 hover:bg-teal-dark/30 text-barrel-gray py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm">
              Voir le Code
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Basic -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-coral/30 p-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Basic</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">29<span class="text-lg text-barrel-gray/60">€/mois</span></p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Par instance</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Support email
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Reponse sous 72h
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Heures ouvrables
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://console.barrel-db.eu/subscribe/basic" class="block w-full text-center bg-coral hover:bg-coral-dark text-white py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm font-semibold">
              S'abonner
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Standard -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-coral/30 p-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Standard</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">99<span class="text-lg text-barrel-gray/60">€/mois</span></p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Par instance</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Support 8x5
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Reponse sous 24h
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Aide au deploiement
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://console.barrel-db.eu/subscribe/standard" class="block w-full text-center bg-coral hover:bg-coral-dark text-white py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm font-semibold">
              S'abonner
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Professional -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-coral p-6 relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-coral text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold">
              Populaire
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Professional</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">249<span class="text-lg text-barrel-gray/60">€/mois</span></p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Par instance</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Support 24x5
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Reponse critique 4h
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Tickets prioritaires
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://console.barrel-db.eu/subscribe/professional" class="block w-full text-center bg-coral hover:bg-coral-dark text-white py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm font-semibold">
              S'abonner
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Enterprise -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Enterprise</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">Sur mesure</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Contactez-nous</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Support 24x7
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                SLA personnalise
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Ingenieur dedie
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/fr/contact" class="block w-full text-center bg-teal-dark/20 hover:bg-teal-dark/30 text-barrel-gray py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm">
              Contacter les Ventes
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Managed Hosting Section -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-teal-light/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Hebergement Gere</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-center mb-8">Laissez-nous le faire tourner pour vous. Infrastructure 100% europeenne.</p>

        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-teal-light/30 p-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">5<span class="text-xl text-barrel-gray/60">€/Go/mois</span></p>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 mb-6">Hebergement de base de donnees gere sur infrastructure europeenne</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm text-left max-w-md mx-auto">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Sauvegardes automatiques
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Haute disponibilite
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Monitoring et alertes
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Centres de donnees UE uniquement (Paris, Amsterdam, Geneve, Lille)
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://console.barrel-db.eu" class="inline-block bg-teal-light hover:bg-teal-dark text-barrel-black px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition font-semibold">
              Ouvrir la Console
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What's Included Section -->
      <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto border border-teal-dark/30 mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-8">Tous les Plans Incluent</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Residence des Donnees UE Uniquement</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Les donnees ne quittent jamais l'infrastructure europeenne</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">100% Open Source</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Apache 2.0. Forkez, modifiez, deployez.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Haute Performance</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Recherche vectorielle &lt;5ms, lectures documents &lt;1ms</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Conforme RGPD</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Concu pour la protection des donnees europeenne</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Questions ?</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-lg border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Puis-je tout auto-heberger ?</h4>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">
              Oui. Barrel Vector et Barrel Docs sont tous deux open source sous licence Apache 2.0. Vous pouvez les executer sur votre propre infrastructure sans cout.
              Les plans payants ajoutent le support professionnel et l'hebergement gere.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-lg border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Que signifie "par instance" ?</h4>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">
              Chaque noeud de base de donnees en cours d'execution compte comme une instance. Si vous executez 3 noeuds Barrel Vector et 2 noeuds Barrel Docs,
              cela fait 5 instances. Combinez les niveaux de support selon vos besoins.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-lg border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Proposez-vous une facturation annuelle ?</h4>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">
              Oui. Les plans annuels incluent 2 mois gratuits. Contactez les ventes pour les tarifs annuels.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-lg border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Comment fonctionne l'hebergement gere ?</h4>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">
              Inscrivez-vous sur <a href="https://console.barrel-db.eu" class="text-teal-light hover:underline">console.barrel-db.eu</a>,
              creez votre base de donnees, et nous gerons le deploiement, les sauvegardes, le monitoring et les mises a jour. Vous recevez les identifiants de connexion
              et nous nous occupons du reste.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</LayoutFr>
